   NEWARK
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
THE PRUDENTIAL Insurance Company of America said it was no longer actively
seeking to sell its subsidiary, Prudential Reinsurance, in a private
transaction, Reuter reports from Newark.
'Prudential Reinsurance is a very valuable business with a strong industry
reputation,' Mr William Link, executive vice-president, in a statement.
